Comparable, Proxy
public class TransitionProxy
extends ElementProxy
implements Comparable

A transition of an automaton. This class represents simple transitions labelled by a single event, leading from a source state to a target state.

Author:
Robi Malik

Returns a hash code value for this element. This is an implementation of the hashCode() function as documented in the Java API. Care has been taken to satisfy the general hashCode() contract, so the hash code does only depend on the immutable members of an element. As a consequence, the method is not always as effective as might be desired.
